<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/free/FP/TragedyCommons.html 204.71.237.74 19970108104425 text/html 17700
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 10:44:40 GMT
Last-modified: Saturday, 28-Sep-96 23:09:25 GMT
