HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 15:14:52 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:13:21 GMT
Content-length: 6789
Content-type: text/html
