http://www.cpac.org:80/free/ST92/NewShade92.html 204.71.237.74 19970108151839 text/html 7336
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 15:18:54 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:09:26 GMT
Content-length: 7150
Content-type: text/html
