http://www.cpac.org:80/mrc/cyberalert/cyb0925.html 204.71.237.74 19970108152246 text/html 5767
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 15:23:03 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 03-Oct-96 17:03:48 GMT
