<DOCNO>WT19-B22-146</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000257-B017-380</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/mrc/medianomics/septrain.html 204.71.237.74 19970108154347 text/html 5054
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
