HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:02:59 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 25-Sep-96 15:04:12 GMT
Content-length: 1833
Content-type: text/html
