<IMG ALIGN=left SRC="/nationalreview/images/mrsmajor.gif">
<H2>WILL MRS. MAJOR GO TO HELL?</H2>
<BR>
<h3><I>John Leonard; Aloise Buckley Heath; William F. Buckley Jr.</I></h3>
<BR>
<P>
Tender, poignant, warm,<BR> and funny, the collected work of the late<BR> Aloise Buckley Heath makes a wonderful gift.<BR>  Trenchant social commentary, along with hilarious vignettes of <I>real</I> family values.
<p>
1990  Book<BR>$16.95        
<P>
<center><a href="order.html">How to Order</a></center> 
<p>
<BR>
<P>
<BR>
