<H2>NATIONAL REVIEW PREMIER ISSUE</H2>
<BR>
<H3><I>William F. Buckley Jr. - editor</I></H3>
<BR>
<p>
The special keepsake is an artful<BR> remembrance of the magazine<BR> that launched the modern conservative movement.<BR>   A commemorative reprise of the original November 19, 1955,<BR> first issue of the publication that stands athwart history, yelling Stop!<BR>  A must-have for every conservative!
