http://www.cpac.org:80/nationalreview/25nov96/rusty.html 204.71.237.74 19970108161922 text/html 4783
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:19:33 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 11-Nov-96 17:47:39 GMT
Content-length: 4597
