<html>
<head>
<BODY bgcolor=lightslategray>
<title>Letter From Al -- November 11, 1996</title>
</head>
<body>
<p>
<center><img src="/nationalreview/images/letter.gif" ALT="Letter From Al"></center>
<p>
<hr> 
<!----------------October 9, 1996---------------------------------->
<P>
<!------------Dear Rusty---------------------------------------------->
<P>
<!------------------------------------------------------------------------->


<BR>
<BR>
<P>

<!-----------------------rusty------------------------------------------------>

Mr. ANONYMOUS BUDDHIST, The Buddhist Temple,<br>
Hacienda Heights, California<br> 
Dear Mr. ANONYMOUS BUDDHIST:<br> 
President Clinton and I wish to thank you for<br>
 your generous contribution of $1500.00<br> 
to the Clinton/Gore '96 Re-Election Campaign.
<p>
As you know, Mr. BUDDHIST, President Clinton<br> 
and I are fighting to protect America's values.<br> 
We can't do it without your support, ANONYMOUS,<br>
and the support of the BUDDHIST family.
<p> 
Once again, thank you, ANONYMOUS BUDDHIST,<br>
for your generous contribution of MAXIMUM<br> 
ALLOWABLE PERSONAL to our effort!
<br> 
Sincerely,<br> 
Al Gore<br>
Vice President of the United States 
<P>
<hr>
<P>
